“person of a <span class="match">country</span> of <span class="match">concern</span>” means: 
 (i) any individual that is not a United States person and is a citizen or permanent resident of a <span class="match">country</span> of <span class="match">concern</span>; 
 (ii) any entity organized under the laws of a <span class="match">country</span> of <span class="match">concern</span> or with a principal place of business in a <span class="match">country</span> of <span class="match">concern</span>; 
